<?xml version="1.0"?>
<package>
  <metadata>
    <id>AdaptableMapper</id>
    <version>0.16.0-beta20191205-01_unreleased</version>
    <title>AdaptableMapper</title>
    <authors>Davey van Tilburg</authors>
    <owners>Davey van Tilburg</owners>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <projectUrl>https://github.com/DaveyvanTilburg/XPathSerialization</projectUrl>
    <description>
A package for any to any mapping without hard-coding

See https://github.com/DaveyvanTilburg/AdaptableMapper/ for documentation
    </description>
    <copyright>Copyright 2019</copyright>
    <dependencies>
      <group targetFramework="net472">
        <dependency id="Newtonsoft.Json" version="12.0.2" />
      </group>
    </dependencies>
    <releaseNotes>
      - Order properties of CompareCondition to form an comparison
      - ReplaceValueMutation property renamed
      - ReplaceValueMutation now checks if it is correctly composed
      - Add Xml CData support
      - Introduce the concept of MappingConfiguration scopes caches
      - Add XmlSetGeneratedIdValueTraversal
      - Removed giving error on empty result for GetValueTraversal implementations
      - Added NotEmptyCondition
      - Bug fix for Xml namespaceless path traversal for attributes
      - Changed build settings for debug and release
      - GetTemplate no longer gets called if the scope traversal finds nothing
      - Bugfix for xml namespaceless traversal for getting attribute from current element
      - Support xpath methods wrapping the path while using namespaceless interpretation
      - bugfix for xmlinterpretation default and xpathmethods
      - Added new generic get block: IfAEmptyThenBElseCGetValueTraversal
      - Changed Empty comparison in IfAEmptyThenBElseCGetValueTraversal with a condition
      - Renamed IfAEmptyThenBElseCGetValueTraversal to IfConditionThenAElseBGetValueTraversal
      - Change list of conditions to have evaluation settings
      - Change the constructor for list of conditions
      - Extend CompareCondition and CompareOperation with LessThan and GreaterThan
      - Add contains comparison operator
      - Switched around order in which scopes and mappings are processed
      - Add ToUpper and ToLower value mutations
      - XmlGetSearchValueTraversal bug fix for no result on actual path
      - Added GetValueTraversalDaysBetweenDates traversal
      - Added CreateSeparatedRangeFromNumberValueMutation
      - Added some null checks to XElementToStringObjectConverter
      - Removed all getsearch implementations with a generic one
      - Introduced the concept of 'compositions'
      - Introduced an abstraction between serialized type reference to actual object type to create a more loosely coupled structure and backwards compatibility after name/space changes
      - Made an abstract implementation for retrieval of list values
      - Renamed XXXGetScopeTraversal to XXXGetListValueTraversal
      - Renamed GetScopeTraversal to GetListValueTraversal
      - Renamed XmlGetNumberOfHits to GetNumberOfHits
      - Made indentation configurable for XElementToStringObjectConverter
      - Added option to exclude declaration for xml
    </releaseNotes>
    <license type="file">License.txt</license>
  </metadata>
  <files>
    <file src="License.txt" />
  </files>
</package>